## üéØ SESSION MANAGEMENT

### **UPDATE DOCUMENTATION WHEN:**
- Progress tracker after every completed subtask
- Schema documentation when modifying database models
- Technical architecture when adding new patterns/conventions
- Implementation strategy when changing development workflows

### **ONE MICRO-TASK FOCUS:**
- Work on only one micro-task per session
- Complete all subtasks before moving to next micro-task
- Update progress tracker with real-time completion status
- Test all functionality before marking complete

Remember: FlyOverseas serves millions globally with zero downtime requirements, premium user experience, and sophisticated AI-powered automation. Every line of code must meet enterprise-grade standards for security, performance, and maintainability.